    <item>
      <title>英国能源供应商尽管有强制要求，但仍出现 19 亿英镑的赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/uk-energy-suppliers-run-a-1-9-billion-deficit-despite-mandates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据周三发布的一份报告，英国国内电力供应商未能满足能源危机后为防止破产而实施的财务要求，缺乏 19 亿英镑（23 亿美元）的现金储备来偿还消费者债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/uk-energy-suppliers-run-a-1-9-billion-deficit-despite-mandates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:22:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Welspun Living 首席执行官谈可持续发展和性别平等</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/welspun-living-ceo-on-sustainability-gender-parity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Welspun Living 首席执行官兼董事总经理 Dipali Goenka 在新加坡举行的 2024 年彭博可持续商业峰会上与彭博社的 Avril Hong 分享了她如何将包容性增长作为这家纺织巨头商业战略的核心。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-31/welspun-living-ceo-on-sustainability-gender-parity</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 16:13:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰晤士水务公司被标准普尔评为垃圾级，穆迪则将该公司评级下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/s-p-cuts-thames-water-s-top-ranked-bonds-to-junk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务金融有限公司 (Thames Water Utilities Finance Plc) 的顶级债券周三被标准普尔全球评级 (S&amp;P Global Ratings) 降至垃圾级，该评级机构警告称，该公司的流动性问题短期内不太可能改善。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/s-p-cuts-thames-water-s-top-ranked-bonds-to-junk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 15:28:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议召开之际债券市场上涨，9 月降息在即</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/treasuries-rally-into-fed-meeting-with-a-september-cut-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受经济数据的推动，美国国债市场在美联储即将公布政策声明之前出现上涨，这强化了人们对美联储将在 9 月再次开会时开始降息的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/treasuries-rally-into-fed-meeting-with-a-september-cut-at-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 14:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员预期美联储将发出降息信号，新兴资产上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/china-stocks-spur-emerging-market-gauge-as-focus-moves-to-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受市场预期美联储周三将维持利率不变但同意在 9 月份降息，这提振了风险偏好，新兴市场股市和货币上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/china-stocks-spur-emerging-market-gauge-as-focus-moves-to-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 11:46:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ares 私人信贷池规模达 340 亿美元，创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/ares-breaks-private-credit-record-with-new-34-billion-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Ares Management Corp. 为其最新的直接贷款基金筹集了近 340 亿美元，这是蓬勃发展的私人信贷市场中最大的专用基金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/ares-breaks-private-credit-record-with-new-34-billion-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 31 Jul 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
